---
title: Creamy Prawn and Chickpea Korma with Basmati Rice, Peas and Sesame Seeds
description: A comforting and mildly spiced Indian favourite, korma sauce pairs well with any kind of veg or protein. Here, this veg-filled version heroes chickpeas and prawns and will be on your table in less than 25 minutes.
